---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Title from "../shared/Title.astro";
---

<section>
  <Container className="space-y-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <Title> About Book World Trip </Title>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
      <div
        class="w-1/3 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-black gap-3"
      >
        <img
          class="w-72 aspect-square rounded-full"
          src="/images/about1.jpg"
          alt=""
        />
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Story</div>
        <div class="text-center">
          We started Book World Trip with a simple goal: to help people explore
          the world. Our team of experienced travel experts work tirelessly to
          craft unique and unforgettable experiences for our clients.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-1/3 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-black gap-3"
      >
        <img
          class="w-72 aspect-square rounded-full"
          src="/images/about2.jpg"
          alt=""
        />
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Services</div>
        <div class="text-center">
          At Book World Trip, we offer a wide range of services to make your
          travel experience as smooth and stress-free as possible. From flight
          bookings to hotel reservations, we have got you covered.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-1/3 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-black gap-3"
      >
        <img
          class="w-72 aspect-square rounded-full"
          src="/images/about3.jpg"
          alt=""
        />
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Destinations</div>
        <div class="text-center">
          With Book World Trip, you can travel to some of the most exotic and
          breathtaking destinations on the planet. Whether you want to explore
          ancient ruins or soak up the sun on a tropical beach, we have a
          destination that's perfect for you.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
